Global Fecal Occult Blood (FOBT) Rapid Diagnostic Test Market Insights
Fecal Occult Blood (FOBT) Rapid Diagnostic Test Market size was valued at USD 0.75 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.2 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Fecal Occult Blood (FOBT) Rapid Diagnostic Test Market Overview
The global Fecal Occult Blood (FOBT) Rapid Diagnostic Test Market is valued at USD 1.15 billion in 2024 and is expected to grow at a CAGR of 7.6%, reaching USD 2.12 billion by 2030. This growth is driven by the increasing prevalence of colorectal cancer, rising awareness about early-stage screening, and technological advancements in diagnostic tools. The market is highly competitive, with key players investing in research and development to improve test sensitivity and specificity. Factors such as an aging population and the growing adoption of home-based diagnostics are anticipated to further propel market growth.

